info.name: Enzy YouTube - Different visited links color
info.description:
- Alternate dark effect for youtube with black and red theme
- Differentiate link colors for visited and unlisted pages or videos
- Annotation are forcefully switched off
info.additionalInfo:
- Switch to theater mode near the player settings for even better view
- To reset visited link colors, clear history in your browser
- Theme has be switched off to enable annotation
